Your wheels should both be vertical, but with age, the trailing arms
sometimes twist and the wheel angles.  No adjustment for this, you need to
replace the arm, or live with the lean.  It may wear the tire some, but
other than that, there really isn't any problem.

> 68 Kombi
>
